Given that we are now in the final-decision window and we do not have a confirmed commitment from any higher-priority family, we are ready to finalize our remaining place based on who is available now. On that basis, we are pleased to offer you the place at Nursery_C.

Please reply to confirm your acceptance and we will proceed immediately with the enrollment paperwork and start-date arrangements.
conversation.thought: Nursery_C has quota 1 and true priority order: B > A > D > E > C. Parent_E is 4th. However, no higher-priority parents (B/A/D) have contacted Nursery_C in any round; given parents' preferences, B and C list Nursery_C as 2nd, D lists it last, A lists it last. By round 28, it is increasingly unlikely that B/A/D will pivot to Nursery_C, and holding out risks ending unmatched. Parent_E has repeatedly and credibly committed to accept immediately and has Nursery_C as first choice, making the match secure. Therefore accept now to fill the seat and avoid ending unfilled.
